.TH BT-JOY-SERVER.SERVICE 8 "2026-05-18" "bt-joy 0.0.6" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
bt-joy-server.service \- systemd unit for the bt-joy MSP server
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B bt-joy-server.service
runs the MSP server using
.IR /etc/bt-joy/server.yaml .
The service starts
.B /usr/bin/joy-server
and restarts on failure.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B systemctl enable bt-joy-server.service
Enable the service at boot.
.TP
.B systemctl start bt-joy-server.service
Start the service.
.TP
.B journalctl -u bt-joy-server.service -f
Follow service logs.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /etc/bt-joy/server.yaml
Server configuration.
.TP
.I /lib/systemd/system/bt-joy-server.service
Systemd unit file.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR joy-server (1),
.BR bt-joy-server.yaml (5)
